{
  "name": "XmlDataBinding",
  "summary": "<p>使用 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/XmlDataBinding/XmlDataBinding .htm#XmlDataBinding.LoadSettings\">LoadSettings</a></strong> 方法可初始化 <strong>XmlDataBinding</strong> 对象的设置。</p>\n<p>使用 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/XmlDataBinding/XmlDataBinding .htm#XmlDataBinding.Refresh\">Refresh</a></strong> 方法可刷新数据绑定。</p>\n<p>使用 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/XmlDataBinding/XmlDataBinding .htm#XmlDataBinding.ClearSettings\">ClearSettings</a></strong> 方法可删除数据绑定。</p>\n<p><b class=\"mainheaders\">示例</b></p><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例显示活动工作簿中第一项XmlMap关联绑定的SourceUrl属性值。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> dataBinding = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">XmlMaps</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">DataBinding</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">`XmlMap关联绑定的SourceUrl属性值: <span class=\"hljs-subst\">${dataBinding.SourceUrl}</span>`</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例删除活动工作簿中每项XmlMap关联的数据绑定。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> xmlmaps = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">XmlMaps</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> i = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>; i &lt;= xmlmaps.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>; i++) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> dataBinding = xmlmaps.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(i).<span class=\"hljs-property\">DataBinding</span>\n        dataBinding.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ClearSettings</span>()\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
  "description": "<p>代表用于某个 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/XmlMap/XmlMap .htm#XmlMap.XmlMap\">XmlMap</a></strong> 对象的源数据连接。</p>\n",
  "category": "et",
  "properties": [
    {
      "name": "SourceUrl",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 <strong>String</strong> 值，它代表为指定数据绑定提供源数据的 XML 数据文件或 Web 服务的路径。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例显示活动工作簿中第一项XmlMap关联的数据绑定的路径。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> dataBinding = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">XmlMaps</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">DataBinding</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(dataBinding.<span class=\"hljs-property\">SourceUrl</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例将第一张工作簿中所有XmlMap关联的数据绑定的路径赋值到单元格中。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> xmlMaps = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">XmlMaps</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> i = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>; i &lt;= xmlMaps.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>; i++) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> dataBinding = xmlMaps.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(i).<span class=\"hljs-property\">DataBinding</span>\n        <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Cells</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(i, <span class=\"hljs-number\">9</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = dataBinding.<span class=\"hljs-property\">SourceUrl</span>\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "string",
      "readonly": true
    }
  ],
  "functions": [
    {
      "name": "ClearSettings",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>删除指定的数据绑定。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例删除活动工作簿中第一项XmlMap关联的数据绑定。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> xmlmaps = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">XmlMaps</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> dataBinding = xmlmaps.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">DataBinding</span>\n    dataBinding.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ClearSettings</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例删除第一张工作簿中最后一项XmlMap关联的数据绑定，然后用XML文件对该绑定进行初始化。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> xmlmaps = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">XmlMaps</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> dataBinding = xmlmaps.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(xmlmaps.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">DataBinding</span>\n    dataBinding.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ClearSettings</span>()\n    dataBinding.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">LoadSettings</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;D:\\\\示例\\\\example.xml&quot;</span>)\n    dataBinding.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Refresh</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [],
      "returns": "void"
    },
    {
      "name": "LoadSettings",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>使用 XML 数据文件或数据检索服务连接 (.uxdc) 文件中的设置初始化指定的数据绑定。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例对活动工作簿中最后一项XmlMap关联的数据绑定的设置进行初始化，并刷新该绑定。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> xmlmaps = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">XmlMaps</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> dataBinding = xmlmaps.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(xmlmaps.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">DataBinding</span>\n    dataBinding.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">LoadSettings</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;D:\\\\test.xml&quot;</span>)\n    dataBinding.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Refresh</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例对活动工作簿中每项XmlMap关联的数据绑定设置，分别用不同的XML文件进行初始化。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> xmlmaps = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">XmlMaps</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> i = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>; i &lt;= xmlmaps.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>; i++) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> dataBinding = xmlmaps.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(i).<span class=\"hljs-property\">DataBinding</span>\n        dataBinding.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">LoadSettings</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">`D:/data<span class=\"hljs-subst\">${i}</span>.xml`</span>)\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [
        {
          "name": "Url",
          "type": "string",
          "description": "<p>XML 数据文件的路径。路径以统一资源定位符 (URL) 或通用命名约定 (UNC)（通用命名约定 (UNC)：一种对文件的命名约定，它提供了独立于机器的文件定位方式。UNC 名称使用 &quot;\\\\server\\share\\path\\filename&quot; 这一语法格式，而不是指定驱动器符和路径。）格式指定。</p>\n",
          "optional": false
        }
      ],
      "returns": "void"
    },
    {
      "name": "Refresh",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>使用指定的 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/XmlDataBinding/XmlDataBinding .htm#XmlDataBinding.XmlDataBinding\">XmlDataBinding</a></strong> 对象的当前连接设置检索 XML 数据。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例刷新活动工作簿中第一项XmlMap关联的数据绑定，并判断如果成功导入数据文件，则通知用户。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> xmlmaps = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">XmlMaps</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> dataBinding = xmlmaps.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">DataBinding</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (dataBinding.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Refresh</span>() == xlXmlImportSuccess) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;XML 数据文件已成功导入。&quot;</span>)\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例对活动工作簿中第一项XmlMap关联的数据绑定的设置进行初始化，并刷新该绑定。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> dataBinding = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">XmlMaps</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">DataBinding</span>\n    dataBinding.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">LoadSettings</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;D:\\\\示例\\\\example.xml&quot;</span>)\n    dataBinding.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Refresh</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [],
      "returns": "<p>一个表示该方法结果的 <strong><a href=\"topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/枚举/XlXmlImportResult 枚举.html\">XlXmlImportResult</a></strong> 值。</p>\n"
    }
  ]
}